<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٩٠ ... سُورَةُ البَلَدِ ... آياتها ٢٠ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَا أُقْسِمُ}</span> ... أُقْسِمُ، وَ <span class="c2">(لَا)</span>: لِتَاكِيدِ القَسَمِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْبَلَدِ}</span> ... مَكَّةَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حِلٌّ}</span> ... يَحِلُّ لَكَ مَا تَصْنَعُ بِهِ مِنَ المُقَاتَلَةِ، وَقَدْ أَنْجَزَهُ اللهُ فِي الفَتْح.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَوَالِدٍ وَمَا وَلَدَ}</span> ... قَسَمٌ بِكُلِّ وَالِدٍ، وَبِكُلِّ مَوْلُودٍ، وَمِنْهُمْ آدَمُ - عليه السلام - وَذُرِّيَّتُهُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَبَدٍ}</span> ... شِدَّةٍ وَعَنَاءٍ مِنْ مُكُابَدَةِ الدُّنْيَا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَيَحْسَبُ}</span> ... أَيَظُنُّ؟<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لُّبَدًا}</span> ... كَثِيرًا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَهَدَيْنَاهُ}</span> ... بَيَّنَّا لَهُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{النَّجْدَيْنِ}</span> ... طَرِيقَي الخَيْرِ وَالشَّرِّ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَلَا اقْتَحَمَ}</span> ... فَهَلَّا تَجَاوَزَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْعَقَبَةَ}</span> ... مَشَقَّةَ الآخِرَةِ؛ بِإِنْفَاقِ المَالِ، وَالعَمَلِ الصَّالِحِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَكُّ رَقَبَةٍ}</span> ... إِعْتَاقُهَا مِنَ الرِّقِّ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَسْغَبَةٍ}</span> ... مَجَاعَةٍ شَدِيدَةٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ذَا مَقْرَبَةٍ}</span> ... ذَا قَرَابَةٍ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ذَا مَتْرَبَةٍ}</span> ... مُعْدِمًا لَا شَيْءَ عِنْدَهُ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>